Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like something was dragged there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Detective Yokomizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But somehow, we keep meeting at places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A famous detective makes his appearance at complex cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be pre-destined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll be counting on you again then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The post mortum report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The death was instant, caused by a snapped neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time of death was approximately between 8:00 PM and 1:00 AM last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The corpse was moved immediately after the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:16.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking into account that only his body that touched the ground is wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With him being moved here, and the water being drained from the rock garden at around 9:00 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the time of the crime was between 9:00 PM and 1:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've already figured out the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:38.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no crime impossible for Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who killed the director?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please do not panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} shall now explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, let us run through everyone's alibi once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you went for a drive with Ran at around 11:15 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And returned around 1:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And following Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Hashimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left dinner to return to his office around 8:10 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} remained in the dining room with me until 9:30 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And had remained in his room till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The important point here is Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} finished cleaning up and returned to the main corridor at 8:45 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She remained there until 2:00 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:07:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who had left to view the night scene, was the only one who left the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are no signs of exit from the windows around the mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's not possible to leave the mansion without passing by Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, those who remained in the mansion between 9:00 PM and 1:00 AM, the time of the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} along with Ran, have valid alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, Hashimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were pressed quite harshly by Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for the repayment of a debt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, who had left the mansion to return to the company...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snuck into Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there you killed Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then moved him to this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moved him to this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then used that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A picking rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For retrieving things that fall onto the rock garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, don't tell me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hashimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} carried Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And tied him to the rod like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, Hashimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, lifted the corpse like this-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible, as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only clue is that something was dragged there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are no signs that the rocks in the garden were moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} placed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could we leave already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and I have alibis during the time of crime anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking so just wait quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found this in a trashcan in the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't want the records of your accounting fraud exposed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring this note with you to the rooftop of the mansion at 11:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} must have been murdered in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in the mansion, Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it was you who—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I am Tanuma's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was Tanuma the driver who died in the accident with the previous director?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I started working here after I heard rumors of Majima setting up the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To confirm the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knows about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was about 10:40 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:10:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said to pay up if I didn't want Majima to know my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, she was looking at her father's picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what time did Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little after 11:00 PM, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you couldn't have noticed if Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too much of a coincident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we will know eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, let's have a look at the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rock garden can be seen clearly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who murdered Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the culprit is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are the culprit, Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:16.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went to Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and closed the curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that she wouldn't notice Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} coming to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you headed to the roof and killed Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And using a device you had prepared here, you moved Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to the rock garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what's the device?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's archery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You prepared an arrow with a loop at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, pulled a long rope through the loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Retaining both ends of the rope, you shot the arrow to the big tree in the rock garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a simple task for a previous national sportsman like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tied the rope to Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and glided him to the rock garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what about the rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tie one end of the rope to the arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just shoot it toward the woods behind the rock garden, and the rope disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would even bet my reputation as a detective on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should be an arrow with a rope attached to it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you should say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found the archery set in Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the arrow was found in the woods behind the rock garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Uncle was right, the corpse wouldn't have ended up that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How exactly did the archery and rope-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ticket to Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s photo exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my deduction is right, that person is still hiding that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be disposed of easily, after all
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that's left is proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that stain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've found it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conclusive proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was giving such an awesome display, what's with Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Important matter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take over from here, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll talk at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wants everyone to gather at the rock garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the rock garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something about finding the true culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the culprit Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you said was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did think of killing Majima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Majima never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.61,0:16:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that, Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone else is the true culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They knew of your plan and used that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The true culprit, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, don't you think it's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The archery aside, if Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was really the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he throw away the threatening letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The letter was taken from Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room and thrown outside to reveal Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, if the corpse was moved from the rooftop as we had deduced earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how he was dangled from a rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The corpse wouldn't be lying face down with his hands and legs arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how was it done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An air mat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that about, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime was probably committed around 8:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when the rock garden fills up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit tied a rope to the air mat, and floated Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body on the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soon after, drainage began and the water receded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And right before the air mat hit the sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They shoved Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body with the picking rod, while pulling back the air mat with all their might
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that, it was possible to place the corpse in the middle of the rock garden without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, marks were left on the rocks at the edge of the pool when the air mat was dragged out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, at that time, it probably washed out from Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a ticket to the photo exhibition ended up stuck in the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upon close inspection...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This scratch mark on the air mat was without a doubt from a button on Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, who is the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit probably panicked when we suddenly came by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} canceled his plans, it would have been all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was why when Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was supposed to meet with Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the culprit took us outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the culprit is-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit took Ran and Conan outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} could carry out his plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiyama Tomonori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:19:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left the dining hall, he did not return to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But went to the main wing of the house and killed Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was still in the dining hall, so there was no worry that he would be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to float the body in the rock garden, Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just kept waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to close Ayaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In brief, Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} intended to conceal Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s movements...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But had assisted in Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s criminal act instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that air-mat was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was found in Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, just hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be a culprit who's trying to pin the crime on me with the air mat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you don't remember seeing the air mat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never seen this air mat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, could you take a closer look at the air mat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's from the memento that you said never left your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ink from your father's fountain pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never imagined it would scatter on the air mat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:38.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I had wiped it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you hadn't done it, Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would have gotten to Majima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He proudly spoke of it with amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Majima messed with the brakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And had my father fall to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while I was away, he made himself the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And took over my father's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I learned of that, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would kill this guy one day, with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} gave me the perfect opportunity to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I consecrated his corpse to the rock garden that my father loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The perfect opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of gas again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do on a mountain road like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll just get picked up by some director again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And get invited to a director's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get to drink good sake again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't need beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this old man talking about?
